passage_text: Newfypoo Size. The newfypoo is a large dog breed. They will reach full size (60-130 pounds) around 24 months of age. The adult size of the newfypoo is dependent upon the size of the parent's used in breeding.

The newfypoo is generally a large dog breed, but the adult size of the newfypoo is generally dependent upon the type poodle used in breeding. Since most newfypoos are bred with standard poodles, the offspring is almost always a large dog that weighs between 60-130 pounds and is 21-30 inches tall from ground to shoulder. The breed is considered loyal, calm, and highly intelligent.

The breed mix is considered a hypoallergenic dog breed. Allergens can also be found in a dogs saliva and dander.
